milestones.description: Tendulkar and Ganguly's 252-run partnership is IND's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 188 between Ravi Shastri and Srikkanth
Tendulkar and Ganguly's 252-run partnership is the highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 225 between Chudasama and Otieno
This is the highest match aggregate (608) involving teams India & Sri Lanka in ODIs
